app.use((req, res, next) => {
  if (req.headers['x-forwarded-proto'] !== 'https') {
    return res.redirect(301, `https://${req.hostname}${req.originalUrl}`);
  }
  next();
});
```

---

### 9. 🟡 No Security Logging or Monitoring
**OWASP A09:2021 — Security Logging & Monitoring Failures | Severity: Medium**

There is no access logging, no audit trail of who accessed `/users`, and no alerting on anomalies.

