|---|-------|---------------|----------|
| 1 | No authentication on `/users` | A01 – Broken Access Control | 🔴 Critical |
| 2 | PII exposed without authorization | A02 – Sensitive Data Exposure | 🔴 High |
| 3 | Missing security headers | A05 – Security Misconfiguration | 🔴 High |
| 4 | No rate limiting | A04 – Insecure Design | 🟠 Medium-High |
